n\nasymptotic linear expansion and facilitates inference on low dimensional\ncomponents of $\\boldsymbol{\\theta}_0$. Finally, we discuss various of choices\nof high dimensional parametric/semi-parametric working models for the PS and OR\nestimators. All results are validated via detailed simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2019 05:11:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-27"}
