aration of the older secondary is not possible in our\nmodel due to the deficiency of free energy needed for an escape of the large\nsecondary. This could be due to an error in the H value of the secondary or the\npossibility that we did not find the real primary of this cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2019 14:50:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Nov 2019 01:54:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-02"}
